University Library


Services


Corporate Membership Services






Corporate Membership Services
Services for corporations and individuals
Corporations and individuals may pay an annual fee to gain circulation privileges for print materials held by the UIC Libraries.
 
The collection of the UIC Law Library is not included in the scope of this program. This membership program does not offer access to other UIC Library services.  No off-site access to library databases is provided.






            Corporate Membership Cards
          Heading link



 
Copy link



Private-sector patrons may borrow materials from the UIC Library, with some limitations.
Getting your card

Please fill out the form below.
Your card will be mailed to the address you provide.
You will be able to borrow items once you have received the card.

Please double check your address in your application.  If your card is returned to us as undeliverable, you may not be eligible to reapply.
Fee Structure

Individual or one corporate membership: $500
Replacement card: $30

Your card responsibilities

You may be billed for overdue or lost items and your library borrowing privileges will be suspended for failure to adhere to Library policies.






